    <item>
      <title>日本加强对更多芯片和量子技术的出口管制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/japan-tightens-export-controls-on-more-chip-and-quantum-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本表示，计划扩大对四种半导体或量子计算相关技术的出口限制，这是全球控制战略技术流动的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/japan-tightens-export-controls-on-more-chip-and-quantum-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 08:38:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Darktrace 同意以 53.2 亿美元出售给 Thoma Bravo</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/darktrace-agrees-to-sale-to-thoma-bravo-for-5-32-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于英国的网络安全公司 Darktrace Plc 表示，同意以约 53.2 亿美元的股权价格将自己出售给私募股权公司 Thoma Bravo。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/darktrace-agrees-to-sale-to-thoma-bravo-for-5-32-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 07:20:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
