      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 06:16:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美团点评首次进驻利雅得，首次向中国以外扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/meituan-to-debut-in-riyadh-as-expansion-beyond-china-quickens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美团点评正计划在沙特阿拉伯首都推出其国际食品配送平台，这是其在国内市场增长放缓之际首次走出大中华区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/meituan-to-debut-in-riyadh-as-expansion-beyond-china-quickens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 04:10:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科塔克银行的失败表明印度科技野心的陷阱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/kotak-bank-s-stumbles-show-pitfalls-of-india-s-tech-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪希望向世界出口印度的数字支付系统。由于印度银行使用的笨重技术无法跟上他的雄心，该计划现在面临着失败的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/kotak-bank-s-stumbles-show-pitfalls-of-india-s-tech-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 02:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
